captions.text: Alright, it is the night before Halloween.
It is getting pretty close to Midnight.
My Dad and I are going to scare the SHIT...
It is going to be exciting.
Get away from me! Get away from me!
Get the fuck out of here!
Oh, did you...are you having a very happy Halloween?
Do you really think this is funny...?
I was dead asleep and you come in...
Quit your crying. It was only freaking ketchup.
And Dad?! You are going to be a part of this too?
Of course! And who is that?
You got me covered in ketchup. Now I am disgusting!
Dad, my friend and my brother...they...they...
Now I am covered in ketchup...
I am sorry! I am sorry, Jess!
I think...My job is done. WOOHOO!
I am going to get a bath!
